title: Jason Sudeikis, Brendan Hunt & Joe Kelly | Damning New Details of Trump's Coup Attempt Revealed in Senate Report: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at a Senate report that provides damning new details about Donald Trump’s attempts to get the Justice Department to overturn the 2020 election.

Jason Sudeikis, Brendan Hunt and Joe Kelly talk about writing Season 3 of Ted Lasso and explain the origins of the show.
